text: Dagar som kommer och går is a studio album from Swedish dansband Kikki Danielssons orkester, formerly known as Kikki Danielsson & Roosarna. It was released in 1998. ==Track listing== ==Svensktoppen== *The title track "Dagar som kommer och går" (Swedish: "Days who come and pass"), whose theme is to find happiness all the seasons of the year and save the time who gives good memories, failed to enter Svensktoppen. == References == Category:1998 albums Category:Roosarna albums
title: Dagar som kommer och går
